LEGEND MOVIE POSTERS CORPORATION, a Nevada corporation, and Xingling Hu, a New Jersey resident, Plaintiffs-Petitioners,
v.
JERRY OHLINGER'S MOVIE MATERIAL STORE, INC., and Jerry Ohlinger, Defendants-Respondents. C-860 September Term 2018
082072 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 14, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003553-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
